videos.description: Down 98-95, Jamal Murray drains a 3-pointer and the Nuggets send the game vs. the Suns to overtime.

videos.headline: Murray sends game to OT with 3

videos.description: Jae Crowder gets the ball in the final seconds of overtime and connects on a 3-pointer to extend the game.

videos.headline: Crowder's off-balance 3 sends game to 2OT

videos.description: Jamal Murray sends the game to overtime and seals it in the second OT, sending the Nuggets to a 120-112 victory vs. the Suns.
